apps.title: TurboTax: File Your Tax Return
apps.description:
"FILE NOW—EVEN AFTER THE DEADLINE.
• Missed the 2024 tax deadline or still need to file? We can help. TurboTax lets you e-file, right on your phone, until October 31, 2025 at 9 PM PST. IRS late penalties may apply. 
• No lines. No waiting. With TurboTax Live Full Service, an expert can do your taxes from start to finish as soon as today. 

CHOOSE HOW MUCH EXPERT HELP YOU WANT
• TurboTax Live Full Service - Let an expert do your taxes start to finish. They can even file your taxes as soon as today! Get matched with an expert based on your unique tax situation. They’ll handle your taxes from start to finish, in real time, and only sign and file when they know your return is 100% correct and you’re getting the best outcome possible (1). 
• TurboTax Live Assisted - File your own taxes, with on-demand expert help as you go. Experts can answer your questions, explain your taxes, and help you fix any mistakes. Once you’re done, get an expert final review so you know it’s done 100% right (1). 
• File your own taxes with confidence - Add your forms and answer a few simple questions, then we’ll guide you from there. When you’re done, CompleteCheckTM reviews your return for 100% accuracy, guaranteed (1).  
• TurboTax Free Edition - $0 federal returns + $0 state returns = $0 to file. ~37% of taxpayers qualify. Simple Form 1040 returns only (no schedules except for Earned Income Tax Credit, Child Tax Credit and Student Loan Interest). (2)

DONE RIGHT, HOWEVER YOU CHOOSE TO FILE
• TAX RETURN LIFETIME GUARANTEE: Whether you get expert help or file yourself, you’ll get your max refund, 100% accuracy, and audit support for your return’s full 7-year lifetime, guaranteed (1).
• DONE RIGHT, WITH OUR TAX EXPERTS: When you work with a TurboTax Live tax expert, you get so much more behind the scenes. Like specialized tax analysts arming your expert with the latest deductions and credits and our quality review team that proactively scans for accuracy. 

FILE EASILY WITH SPECIAL APP FEATURES
• File 30% faster on our app!* 
• Get started quickly with easy info uploads. Snap a photo, upload your docs, or import your forms directly from your employer or financial institution, and we’ll auto-fill your info.
• Spanish-language support: You can now toggle between English and Spanish and file your taxes in your preferred language. Bilingual experts are also available to help you file your taxes or do them for you.

ALREADY FILED? WE'RE STILL HERE TO HELP
• TurboTax Live customers get unlimited expert help year-round, at no extra cost
• Need to amend? We can help you accurately file your amended taxes easily and with confidence. 

DISCLAIMERS 
*On average, customers using our mobile app take 30% less time to complete their taxes compared to time taken on our website
1. Guarantees: See terms of service or turbotax.com/guarantees for full details.
2. TurboTax Free Edition: TurboTax Free Edition is available for those filing simple Form 1040 returns and limited credits only (no forms or schedules except for the Earned Income Tax Credit, Child Tax Credit and student loan interest), as detailed in the TurboTax Free Edition disclosures. Roughly 37% of taxpayers qualify. Offer may change or end at any time without notice.
3. Intuit is an independent company with no affiliation to any government entity. This TurboTax app also doesn't represent any government entity. The websites for the IRS: https://www.irs.gov, as well as state & local tax authorities listed here: https://ttlc.intuit.com/turbotax-support/en-us/help-article/state-taxes/contact-state-department-revenue/L9qVToi02_US_en_US are the source of information for specific tax requirements. 
Intuit has offices worldwide, and is headquartered in Mountain View, 2700 Coast Ave, Mountain View, CA 94043."

apps.title: Investor's Business Daily
apps.description:
Winning stock lists, real-time charts and up-to-the-minute market news: now available everywhere, thanks to the newly enhanced Investor’s Business Daily app.

Investor's Business Daily is proud to have been named "Best Financial Research and Data Company" in the 2023 FinTech Breakthrough Award program.

IBD Digital members now have access to their favorite premium features, IBD premium lists, charts and personal stock lists. Not an IBD member? You’ll still be able to keep up with market news, videos and information like you would on Investors.com.
 
Features:
 
•  Your personal stock lists, now synced across all your devices
•  Access to premium features for all IBD Digital members
•  Exclusive stock lists like IBD 50, Sector Leaders, IPO Leaders and more
•  The latest daily market analysis with The Big Picture and Stock Market Today
•  Customizable stock list on the home screen
•  Personalized news pages with embedded videos to keep you up-to-date on stocks you’re watching
•  Tap stock symbols to see IBD’s exclusive Smart Select Ratings
•  A widget accessible on your device home screen lets you create a personal stock list to see mini-charts, current price/volume and ratings.

•  A native iOS login screen so you can use Face ID/Touch ID.

apps.title: Square Invoices: Invoice Maker
apps.description:
Square Invoices is a must-have invoicing solution to run your business: invoice and estimate maker, and a secure, fast payment system.

It is an essential invoicing solution that efficiently supports any type of business:
► Home & Repair: Contractors, Cleaning, Automotive, Landscaping
► Food & Drink: Catering, Bakery, Food Trucks, Wholesale Stores
► Professional Services: Web Designers, Photographers, Consultants, Accountants, Architects, Interior Designers, Advertising, Real Estate

It has everything you need to run your business on the go: estimates, contacts, invoices, payments, automatic reminders and real-time tracking and reporting. It’s all in one app, and there are no monthly fees. Bill customers with a simple invoice app that also makes sending estimates or requesting deposits easy. Access Square Invoices on your iPhone, iPad or desktop.

► INVOICE AND ESTIMATE MAKER
Send professional invoices and estimates in three simple steps: just enter your customer’s email, the amount, and hit send. Customise the look and easily attach photos, contracts, or receipts.

► ACCEPT ANY KIND OF PAYMENT
Cut collection times from weeks to days by giving your customers more convenient ways to pay—no more stamps or envelopes. Customers can pay online or in person with any major debit or credit card, Apple Pay or Google Pay, cash, check or ACH Payment.

► REACH CUSTOMERS MORE EFFECTIVELY
Send invoices wherever your customers prefer—email, URL, text / SMS, manually through any messaging app, or print out a hard copy. Customers can easily pay on their phone or computer from anywhere.

► AUTOMATIC REMINDERS AND TRACKING
Stop chasing down payments with automatic payment reminders and transparent tracking that tells you the moment each invoice is viewed and paid.

► FLEXIBLE BILLING
Get paid on your schedule by requesting a deposit or setting up recurring invoices for weekly or monthly billing. Customers can also authorize Square to securely save their payment cards on file to be charged automatically.

Whether you are sending a quote to confirm your next freelance job, requesting a deposit for a custom order, or billing for your contractor hours, Square Invoices is the all-in-one app for your payment and workflow needs. Download and set up your account in just minutes.

Love the app? Leave us a rating or review.

Questions? We're here to help: square.com/help.

apps.title: Business tour
apps.description:
Business Tour is a free desktop online game. Gather a team of up to 4 people, play multiplayer games with friends online, complete daily tasks, participate in tournaments with other players, and exchange rewards with future profits.

EASY START, CHALLENGING PATH TO THE TOP
Business Tour allows you to play online games with friends. The main advantage of this game is that it's easy to learn but challenging to win. You'll need to use your sharp mind and entrepreneurial talent to outwit other players and become kings of the board. The game is complex and unpredictable, making it engaging and the gameplay diverse.

PLAY WITH FRIENDS OR SOLO
You can play this game solo against three opponents, invite your friends for team games and compete with two strangers, or invite all your friends to show them who the real business and city-building sharks are. Your main weapon is strategy in this free game board. It doesn't matter whether you or your friends are novices or experienced business sharks; the right strategy will save you even in the most dire situations in this city-building game.

CREATE YOUR UNIQUE STYLE
You can play aggressively or cautiously, choose a moderate monopolistic strategy, go all-in, or combine everything to create a city mania. But how will other players remember you on the monopoly game field? Choose from over 100 unique characters and dice and become the most recognizable monopolist in the world of "Business Tour." You can be a fun pigeon person with ice cube dice in a big city or an inflatable superhero throwing dice in a mystical human game. Or maybe you prefer the classics? Then classic characters with traditional gaming mania are perfect for you to build your city. Collect rent and create your own corporation!

COMPETE EVERY DAY
If you love competitions, free games, and challenges, you can compete with others on the player rankings based on the number of chips in the game on YouTube. Be sure to test your best business skills, tactics, and strategic plans to be at the top of the rankings and the star ratings in megapolises, metropolises, and city horizons by the end of the month. Receive rewards for these achievements and plan your tactics ahead for the next month on the game board!

And if you have any questions about the game, you can go through a detailed tutorial. Don't hesitate to reach out to our support master for assistance and problem-solving.

Key features:

Online multiplayer, 2-4 players
Regular tournaments
Option to link Steam and Google accounts
Daily rewards
Over 100 unique characters and dice
Leaderboards
Daily tasks
Private tables with ID access
Offline mode with bots
Local mode with other players on one screen
Terms of Service: https://8floor.net/tos/

apps.title: Zoho CRM - Sales & Marketing
apps.description:
Zoho CRM empowers empowers over 300,000 businesses across the world businesses in over 180 countries. It 
helps businesses engage with customers, convert more leads, and grow their revenue by 
closing more deals. 
 
Oversee your sales on the move with the Zoho CRM mobile app.  
 
Whether you're a sales rep making calls, a sales manager monitoring the sales pipeline, or a 
business owner nurturing your business, approach your workday efficiently with a state-of-the-
art mobile CRM system.   
 
Your mobile CRM app not only covers your CRM software requirements on the go but also 
helps boost mobile sales productivity with features like search, call, email, check-in, near-me, 
and notifications. With a highly fluid, interactive interface, offline access, and the ability to sync 
data across all your devices automatically, Zoho's mobile CRM is perfect for field sales.  
 
Features : 
 
- Get a clear overview of your scheduled tasks, meetings, and calls. Set reminders so that you 
never miss out on a single one.  
 
- Use the powerful global search to locate anything you need. 
 
- Review notes and attachments before heading out for important meetings.  
 
- Locate customers and sales opportunities nearby and navigate.  
 
- Check in at a client's location to record your visit.  
 
- Know who's calling with the Caller ID feature.  
 
- Log calls and capture the details of your conversation with ease by attaching voice notes.  
 
- Visualize sales and marketing trends and make decisions while you're away from your desk. 
  
- Collaborate with your team in real-time using Feeds and @mention colleagues on posts.  
 
- Sync your data automatically across all platforms without worrying about network connectivity.   
 
 
 
If you have any questions or comments, please write to us at crm@zohomobile.com. We'll be 
happy to help.

https://www.zoho.com/privacy.html

apps.title: Comcast Business
apps.description:
AVAILABLE TO COMCAST BUSINESS CUSTOMERS

Access your Comcast Business account anytime and anywhere with the Comcast Business App—an innovative, all-in-one tool designed with your business in mind. With streamlined navigation and an intuitive layout, the Comcast Business App makes it easier than ever to manage your account on the go, right from your mobile device. 

With the Comcast Business App, you can:

• Manage your account details
• View upcoming service appointments
• Pay your bill, view past invoices, and manage your payment methods
• Enroll in Auto Pay and Paperless Billing
• Manage WiFi networks, hotspots, and more
• Set up notifications for billing and service requests
• Stay up-to-date on your service status
• View your TV channel lineup
• Forward calls to your home, mobile phone, or colleagues with Call Forwarding 
• Troubleshoot technical issues in a few easy steps
• Access Comcast Business Support

These features are available to Business Internet, Business TV, Business Voice, Business Voice Mobility, Business VoiceEdge™, and/or Business VoiceEdge Select™ customers and will vary depending on your services.

Comcast Business Voice Mobility, Business VoiceEdge®, and Business VoiceEdge Select™ customers can also:

• Easily host a conference call for up to 50 participants (Business VoiceEdge® customers only)
• View recent calls, listen to and manage voicemail, and customize greetings 
• Make outgoing calls through the app to display your business phone number on caller IDs
• Quickly transfer calls to colleagues or third parties
• Forward calls to your home, mobile phone, or colleagues with Call Forwarding 
• Quickly move active calls to your Be Anywhere devices and desk phones
• Select the phones that will ring on inbound calls by managing Be Anywhere devices
• Easily manage security settings

These features will vary depending on your services. 

You can submit feedback to CBMA_Feedback@comcast.com

apps.description:
Seamlessly add your business card to your Apple Wallet, which is compatible with iPhone, iPad, and Apple Watch. Social Card revolutionizes how you share your contact information when you meet someone new. Built for business owners, social influencers, and anyone aiming to modernize their networking.

Get Started Today!
Download Social Card and join thousands of professionals who are modernizing their networking experience.

WHY SOCIAL CARD?
Having a business card is a requirement. However, keeping one ready in your wallet is a hassle. Not having one when you need it is even worse.

Social Card helps you digitize your business cards so they are always ready to network everywhere you take your Apple devices.

What you'll love about Social Card:

- Apple Wallet Integration: Store and access your card in your Apple Wallet like an airline boarding pass.
- Effortless Sharing: Your business card is just a click away on your lock screen. You don't need to open an app to share your information, making the process quick and easy.
- Comprehensive Contact Sharing: Our advanced contact cards allow you to share all the essential information in one go, eliminating the need for manual contact entry and ensuring every contact card is completed.
- Links: More than just contact cards. Link to websites, social media profiles, phone numbers, emails, and more.
- Friendly Interface: Getting your business cards to look pixel-perfect should be easy. We've built a simple guided user interface to help you start networking as soon as possible.

FREE Version Includes:
- One FREE Social Card.
- Pre-selected colors.
- Custom headshot image.
- Custom QR code.
- Daily card updates.

PREMIUM Version Unlocks:
- One-time payment. No subscriptions.
- Unlimited card updates.
- Custom colors to match your brand.
- Add your own logo.
- Advanced contact card fields (photo, links, and more customizations)
- Offline contact cards.

Start building your Social Card today and enhance your networking!

apps.title: Payoneer - Business Payments
apps.description:
Take Control of Your Global Payments with Payoneer

Manage your business payments from anywhere with Payoneer, the ultimate platform for global payment solutions. Tailored for small to medium-sized businesses (SMBs), corporate entities, and entrepreneurs, Payoneer makes international money transfers and online payment processing seamless, secure, and cost-effective.

Why Choose Payoneer?

Receive Payments Globally.
Effortlessly send money overseas or receive payments in popular currencies like USD, EUR, GBP, JPY, and more. With Payoneer, you’ll gain access to international payment gateway solutions specifically designed for SMBs. Withdraw funds to your local business bank account in over 150 countries or access them instantly using your Payoneer card.

Simplify Payments for Businesses
Whether you’re paying service providers, suppliers, or contractors, Payoneer’s payment solutions ensure smooth, reliable transactions in over 200 countries. Enjoy fast and affordable digital payment options that help you avoid high fees and delays—allowing your business to operate efficiently.
Manage Finances with Ease

Track and control your finances on the go. 
From monitoring payments to managing balances across multiple currencies, Payoneer provides tools that enhance your financial flexibility and reliability. Competitive currency conversion rates empower you to pay suppliers in their preferred currencies while maximizing your cost savings.
Expand Your Business with Confidence

Leverage seller-specific features like VAT payments in multiple countries and working capital offers for platforms like Amazon and Walmart. Easily scale your business with immediate access to funds while ensuring ongoing cash flow efficiency.

Why Download the Payoneer App?
The Payoneer app makes managing your global payment solutions more convenient than ever. Oversee international money transfers and monitor payment solutions directly from your smartphone, bringing flexibility to your financial operations.

Reliable Customer Support
Our multilingual team is available 24/7 to assist with your digital payment solutions in over 20 languages. Whether you’re troubleshooting or have questions, we’re always just a click away.

Get Started Today
Join millions of businesses worldwide already using Payoneer to simplify their international money transfers and enhance their growth. Download the app now to unlock the power of a truly efficient global payment platform!

Simplify Your Business Expenses
Create up to five expense accounts and give your staff expense cards to organise your spending.

Get A Physical POS Terminal
Accept instant bank transfers and card payments anywhere with a Kuda Business POS.

Make Bulk Transfers
Send different amounts or the same amount to many people at once.

Register Your Business 
Do your CAC registration without hidden charges or legal fees. 

Get Perks
Access discounts on business tools, payment services, healthcare and more. 

Kuda Business is the all-in-one business manager for Nigerian freelancers and SMEs. Open a business bank account, accept transfers and card payments, get a POS, send invoices, manage expenses, make bulk transfers, and pay business bills.

With the Kuda Business app you can: 

1. Open a business bank account in minutes.
2. Accept payments for free with Kuda Business Virtual POS. 
3. Register with the Corporate Affairs Commission(CAC)and upgrade to a full Kuda Business account to get a POS terminal.

Have any questions about creating a business bank account on Kuda Business?

X: @kudabusiness
Instagram: @kudabusiness
Address: Yaba, Lagos

Virtual phone numbers, like email, are 'in the cloud'. They work seamlessly across all of your devices - office phones, cell phones, computers, and landlines. Teams can share a single virtual number too. They come in local & toll-free area codes and are portable.

apps.title: HiHello: Digital Business Card
apps.description:
HiHello: The Best Digital Business Card App

Join the future of networking with HiHello, the leading digital business card app trusted by professionals worldwide. With over a million biz cards shared monthly, HiHello is your essential tool for building and managing valuable business connections.

BEAUTIFUL & CUSTOMIZABLE BUSINESS CARD MAKER
- Make and personalize interactive virtual business cards with different templates, designs, and colors. 
- Create stunning free electronic business cards with profile photos, or transform your vcard into a video business card. 
- Add unlimited content, include links, social media, video, PDF, payment apps, and more. 

EFFORTLESS SHARING
- Share your card with anyone, even if they don’t have the HiHello app. 
- Share with a branded QR code, link, email, SMS, iMessage, Apple Watch, Apple Wallet, Siri, widget, lock screen widgets, social media, Airdrop, NFC, and more.

BUSINESS CONTACT MANAGER
- Your virtual Rolodex that helps you keep track of everyone you meet. 
- Manage your contact list with automated sorting, notes and tags to organize, and a timeline of who you met and when in the smart address book.
- Easily save any HiHello contacts into your phone or preferred contact manager.

AI-POWERED BUSINESS CARD READER, SCANNER, AND TRANSCRIPTION
- Instantly capture any paper card lead with the AI-powered business card scanner.
- Built on multiple AI models with a human verification backup if needed, HiHello is the most accurate business card scanner app. 

VIRTUAL BACKGROUNDS
- Stay on brand in every meeting or presentation with custom virtual backgrounds that link to your smart business cards for virtual meetings or live streaming.
- Create personalized, branded backgrounds with a photo from our library, or upload your own.
- Share what you want with your audience by creating a specific card and virtual background QR code for your meeting or presentation.

EMAIL SIGNATURES
- Create professional, interactive, attention-grabbing signatures that are compatible with any email platform and correspond to your business card of choice.
- Choose from multiple templates and styles.

ANALYTICS 
- Gain valuable insights into card usage, engagement, and lead generation with in-app analytics and data integrations.

INTEGRATIONS 
- Integrate HiHello with the systems that matter most, including SSO, Active Directory, and CRMs like Salesforce and Hubspot.

SECURITY & PRIVACY 
- HiHello is SOC 2 Type 2 compliant and meets the privacy requirements for EU GDPR, UK GDPR, CCPA, and the Australian Privacy Act. 

SCALE TO TEAMS
- Plans built for teams of all sizes.
- Leverage digital business cards, email signatures, and virtual backgrounds to present your brand consistently and generate and capture leads to grow your business.

ABOUT HIHELLO 
HiHello is changing how everyone—from individuals to Fortune 500 companies—manages their most important contacts. It starts with a digital business card built from the ground up to be delightful, customizable, and secure. HiHello’s digital business cards unlock new opportunities, cut the costs of traditional cards, and have a positive environmental impact. Millions of professionals worldwide trust HiHello to amplify the power of their network, and we’re just getting started!

apps.title: North One - Business Banking
apps.description:
North One is a Business Checking Account that simplifies your banking experience, allowing you to focus on what matters most—growing your business.

Simplify your finances with one Account
Access all the essential banking features you need without the usual fees, branch visits, or paperwork.


With the North One app, you can:
- Earn money back on your Mastercard® Small Business Debit Card purchases
- Send and receive payments any time with Standard ACH, Same-day ACH, wire transfers, paper checks⁶, & more
- Apply for a Business Line of Credit and Business Term Loan⁴
- Receive payments instantly from Stripe, Cash App, Square, Amazon, PayPal, Venmo, and more⁵
- Bank anywhere, any time
- Enjoy low fees and high limits
- Buy with physical and virtual debit cards
- Invite your accountant, bookkeeper, and team members
- Free inbound wires
- Give each of your co-owners their own login and debit card
- Millions of ATMs with fee refunds
- Deposit cash at over 90,000 retail locations⁷
- Talk to a local Customer Care expert who understands your business
 
North One is a financial technology company, not a bank. Banking services for the deposit account provided by The Bancorp Bank, N.A., Member FDIC.
 
The NorthOne Mastercard® Small Business Debit Card is issued by The Bancorp Bank, N.A., Member FDIC, pursuant to license by Mastercard International Incorporated. Mastercard and the circles design are registered trademarks of Mastercard International Incorporated. Card may be used everywhere Mastercard is accepted.
 
All trademarks and brand names belong to their respective owners. Use of these trademarks and brand names do not represent endorsement by or association with this card program.

2. Applicable to the North One Standard Plan. Optional North One Plus Plan available for $20/month.
3. North One does not charge a fee for this service, but may reimburse you for third-party fees charged. You must contact the North One Customer Care Team to request reimbursement. Some restrictions apply. 
4. North One is a financial technology company, not a lender. North One does not issue loans or make credit decisions in connection with loans. North One Lending is powered by Kanmon. All loans are subject to credit approval. Your terms may vary. North One Lending loans are issued by Kanmon, a licensed lender. California Loans are made pursuant to a Department of Financial Protection and Innovation California Lenders Law License. Read more about Kanmon at kanmon.com.
5. Real Time Payments are available through The Clearing House Payments Company, LLC and generally occur within seconds, however certain circumstances could result in a delay or cancellation of a payment. See your Deposit Account Agreement for more details.
6. See Deposit Account Agreement for details on ACH transfers, Same-day ACH transfers, mobile check deposit, physical checks, domestic wire transfers, and third party cash transfers (subject to terms and conditions of GreenDot® Corporation).
7. Cash deposits are subject to terms and conditions of Green Dot Corporation. © Green Dot Corporation. Green Dot is a registered trademark of Green Dot Corporation. The retailer that receives your cash will be responsible to transfer the funds for deposit into your North One Account.

apps.title: Privat24 for business
apps.description:
"Privat24 for business" is a mobile application for legal entities and private entrepreneurs. 
Key features:
	•	Account management: view statements, monitor income and spendings, analyze cash flow.
	•	Payments: pay contractors, suppliers, and partners quickly and securely. Payment templates are available for optimization.
	•	Electronic document management: create and send invoices, exchange documents with suppliers.
	•	Currency exchange operations: buy, sell, and convert foreign currency at the current exchange rate without visiting a bank. Enable notifications for the start of the trading session to perform necessary operations timely.
	•	Tax payments: automatically receive data from the State Tax Service, pay taxes, fees, and other mandatory payments. Activate payment deadline reminders to pay on time.
	•	Reporting: sign and submit reports to the State Tax Service within the app, use the Reporting calendar and automatic data completion for tax calculation.
	•	Salary projects: manage salary payments to employees on PrivatBank or other Ukrainian bank cards.
	•	Loans and deposits: monitor the status of loan agreements, apply for new loans, and open / replenish / close deposits online.
	•	Business cards: open corporate cards, track transactions, and set limits.
	•	Notifications: receive instant notifications for all incoming and outgoing funds.
	•	Security: the app has enhanced fraud protection, including the use of device data to prevent unauthorized actions.
	•	Instant login via Face ID / Touch ID.
	•	SmartID: your qualified electronic signature for securely signing payments and documents.
The app includes a special section for connecting with PrivatBank:
	•	Online chat support.
	•	Option to call the bank within the app or request a callback.
	•	Review the history of inquiries to the bank.
	•	Reporting fraud.
	•	Connect via Telegram or Viber.
We also provide sign language consultations via video chat for clients with hearing impairments.
"Privat24 for business" is your reliable assistant for managing your business from anywhere in the world. 
We are constantly improving the functionality and interface. We appreciate your feedback at: p24b_mobile@privatbank.ua

apps.description:
Detailed analytics on the company operation, overall insights for the whole company and by each locality.

•Sales trends–the amount of revenue, quantity and average spend, comparison by period.
•Money reports–balance on accounts, in cash registers and on deposit.
•Cash flow analysis–inflows and outflows, payments to vendors, and employee wages.
•Product rating–by revenue, volume and frequency of sales.
•Cashiers’ efficiency–see your top-sellers and those who are behind, decide on bonuses or penalties.
•Reporting to government agencies–view and file reports, use the Saby calendar to see what to file next, and keep track of document statuses.
•Recognition of primary accounting documents–just take photos or upload your documents. Saby will recognize a consignment note and record the items against a proper warehouse or use the invoice photo to issue a payment order.
•Video surveillance–use your smartphone instead of a video surveillance point, wherever you have the Internet connection.
•All about companies–company details, owners, financial state, business value and other up-to-date information about companies in your region and Russia.
•Notifications–get alerts on cash register issues, receipts with manully entered discounts and other questionable transactions, all with video recordings attached.

apps.title: Business Card Reader
apps.description:
ABBYY Business Card Reader –The World’s Fastest Business Card Scanner & Contact Management App for iPhone and iPad! 

Recommended by The New York Times, CNN, The Telegraph, Computer Business Review, Macworld. 
Winner of the RISING STAR Award in the Mobile Star Awards 

ABBYY Business Card Reader easily & simply captures & stores contact from business cards in 25 languages to your iPhone and iPad. The recognized data can be saved in either your device contacts or the app digital storage.

KEY FEATURES
• QUICK AND ACCURATE SCANNING
ABBYYs optical character recognition technology provides quick & accurate recognition of all contact information: names, organizations, phone numbers, e-mail addresses, etc. 	 
• AUTO-CLICK PHOTO FEATURE
Automatically focuses on the business card, detects its edges, crops any extraneous background & captures an image of the card all by itself. 
• EASY CHECK OF RECOGNIZED DATA
The app highlights “unusual” characters with blue color and displays the original image so that you can quickly confirm the output of the app.
• APPLE WATCH APP. You won’t need to reach for your iPhone or iPad to remember somebody’s name. View contacts and make phone calls right from BCR on your Apple Watch! 
• AUTOMATIC NORMALIZATION OF PHONE AND EXTENTION NUMBERS
BCR will automatically put in all the missing parts so that you can reach the contact even if the country code was omitted in print. 
• AUTOCOMPLETION OF ADDRESSES
BCR corrects any typos and fills in the missing address fields so you can easily find it on the map.
• MANUAL BACKUPS. Manual backups to archive and restore to another device.
• Export contacts to Salesforce Leads (premium account required). BCR can export business cards to Enterprise, Unlimited, and Performance Editions of SF license.  Professional Edition does not allow BCR export. 
• Set up voice commands in Siri Shortcuts app to open business cards by voicing the name of the owner.
• Spotlight Search to find business cards from BCR 
• Export business cards to MS Excel in .CSV format.
• Smart Facebook and LinkedIn search: connect social media account to the business card and auto upload photo of contact from Facebook.
• Search in iPhone Maps for the address of your contacts.
• Exchange digitally and forward recognized contacts via e-mail as VCard or JPEG files or via SMS as a plain text.
• Share your contacts using QR code.
• Support 25 languages including recognition of multilingual cards.
- French
- German
- Greek
- Japanese
- Indonesian
- Italian
- Korean
- Norwegian (both Bokmal and Nynorsk)
- Polish
- Portuguese (Portugal)
- Portuguese (Brazil)
- Russian
- Spanish
- Swedish
- Turkish
- Ukrainian

The free version provides 10 card recognition. Enable Premium to get unlimited functionality:
• Unlimited business card recognition
• Export to Excel
• No ads

Premium Account auto-renewable subscription allows using all functions of this app. Subscription length periods:  1 month with 7 days free trial, and 1 year. The subscription is automatically renewed at the end of the period unless you choose to cancel the subscription at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Payment will be charged to your iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. You can manage your subscription and switch off the auto-renewal by accessing your Account Settings after purchase. Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited if you purchase a subscription to that publication. 

Read us:
abbyy.com/blog/mobile
Facebook.com/ABBYYsoft
Twitter @ABBYY_Software
YouTube.com/ABBYYvideos

Privacy Policy abbyy.com/privacy
Terms of Use abbyybcr.com/en/eula

Looking forward to your feedback on the App Store!

Ramp is the finance automation platform designed to save you time and money. With Ramp you get corporate cards, expense management, bill payments, accounting automation and reporting—all in one easy-to-use solution.

Ramp Mobile puts finance automation in your pocket. Pay for expenses quickly with your corporate card at your fingertips. Submit expense reports and reimbursements on the go by taking a picture of your receipt and tapping in a memo or other submission requirements. - See your expense policy

apps.title: MileIQ: Mileage Tracker & Log
apps.description:
Track and Record Mileage Automatically and Maximize your Tax Reimbursement with MileIQ

MileIQ is the #1 automatic mileage tracker app, trusted by millions of users to simplify productivity, tax preparation, expense tracking, and financial planning. Whether you're self-employed, a small business owner, or part of a team, MileIQ simplifies mileage tracking so you can focus on growing your business. Save time, maximize tax deductions and reimbursements, and generate IRS-compliant reports—without the hassle of manual logs.

Smart, Automatic Mileage Tracking
Stop wasting time on manual mileage logs. MileIQ’s smart mile tracker uses GPS-powered tracking that runs in the background, automatically recording every business and personal drive to streamline your reimbursement. Add custom labels, notes, and purposes to keep your mileage records organized.

Maximize Your Tax Deductions
Turn miles into tax savings with MileIQ. Automatically calculate business and personal mileage. Easily generate IRS-compliant reports for easy write-offs, reimbursements, and Schedule C or 1099 filings. Skip the spreadsheets—export logs in seconds and join millions who’ve saved $10B+ using MileIQ.

Flexible Categorization & Customization
Quickly classify your drives with MileIQ’s smart mile tracker, swiping right for business and left for personal.  Need more control? Customize categories to match your workflow and stay aligned with your unique needs. Boost productivity by keeping everything organized in one app. Add detailed trip purposes like client meetings, supply runs, or business errands to support tax audit readiness.

Key Features of MileIQ:
- Automatic mileage calculator & tracking with smart GPS technology.
- Accurate drive classification for business or personal purposes.
- IRS-compliant mileage reports for tax preparation.
- Exportable summaries to assist with tax filings and financial statements.
- Monthly and annual summaries to simplify financial planning.
- Secure cloud storage to access your recorded data anytime, anywhere.
- User-friendly interface designed for productivity and ease of use provides hassle-free navigation.

Who Can Benefit from MileIQ?
- Freelancers and self-employed professionals: Simplify 1099 tax preparation and focus on growing your business.
- Small business owners: Gain insights into mileage expenses and streamline reimbursements.
- Sales professionals: Track business miles and ensure accurate billing.
- Rideshare and delivery drivers: Maximize deductions and keep accurate records effortlessly.
- Employees with mileage reimbursements: Ensure accurate reporting for reimbursements.
- Tax professionals and bookkeepers: Access organized mileage data to support filings and audits.

Why Choose MileIQ?
- Trusted by millions of users worldwide—Featured in Forbes, Entrepreneur, and The New York Times
- Accurate, reliable, and designed to save you time and money.
- 100 Billion+ Miles Logged
- Users saved $10 Billion+ in Reimbursements
- 80,000+ 5-star reviews for simplicity, functionality, and effectiveness.
- Unlimited mileage tracking with 40 free drives every month

Start Tracking Your Miles Today! Download MileIQ and join a community of professionals saving time and money with smarter mileage tracking. Don’t leave your deductions on the road—make every mile count with MileIQ.

Unlock Premium Features: Upgrade to MileIQ Premium for unlimited mileage tracking, advanced reporting tools, and enhanced productivity features. Start with a free trial and experience the benefits today.

Your Mileage. Your Savings. Take control of your finances with the ultimate mileage tracker app. Download MileIQ now and drive your way to more savings, smarter tax preparation and financial planning.

Start driving smarter today.

Housecall Pro is the top-rated field service management platform built to help run & grow your home services business from the palm of your hand. Save hours a week by going paperless, so you can work on your business, not just for your business. 

Scheduling and Dispatching
• Edit your schedule from desktop or phone
• Manage appointments with a drag & drop calendar
• Set recurring jobs, assign teams, & schedule arrival windows
• Send jobs straight to your techs’ calendars
• Update techs with automatic phone notifications 
• Improve communication with in-app messaging
• Attach notes & photos while out in the field

Customer Communication
• Deliver a 5-star experience
• Send job status updates & on-my-way texts
• Automatically send text and email reminders & confirmations
• Request reviews from your best customers
 
Online Booking

• Customers can directly book your available time slots

Estimates & Invoices
• Create, update, & send invoices & estimates from your computer or phone
• Automatically email estimates, invoices, & receipts
• Customize line items & add services during the job

Payment
• Accept cash, checks, & debit/credit
• Process credit cards quickly through the app
• Send text invoices & let your customers pay via phone
• Directly deposit funds into your bank account
• Close bigger jobs with consumer financing

Marketing
• Send automatic reminder & thank-you emails
• Deliver automated postcards right to customers’ doorsteps

GPS Time Tracking
• See when your team’s at the job site & avoid miscommunications
• Track techs’ locations & schedule them to the closest job

QuickBooks Online Integration
• Import job history, customers, & price list
• Reconcile payments & invoices
• Instantly sync job data into QBO

Advanced Reporting
• Track key data points with customizable reporting widgets
• Drive business insights & optimize marketing

Admin & Security
• Automatically sync data to your secure cloud
• Allow admins to track job status from the office
• Set employee permissions
• Export customer data & job information at any time

apps.title: magicJack for BUSINESS
apps.description:
Reliable phone service. Incredible price. 

magicJack for BUSINESS™ offers everything you need in a business phone system at a fraction of the cost of standard providers. Get fast, reliable service for one low, flat rate per line. The best scalable solution to streamline communications across your business. With our FREE app, you can free yourself from your desk and communicate smarter from anywhere! 

With the magicJack for BUSINESS app, you can make calls to virtually anyone in the world and send SMS text messages over WiFi and 3G/4G/LTE. 

Features included with your service: 
•	Local and long distance calling to the U.S. and Canada*
•	Free Voicemail 
•	Free SMS texting 
•	Free Conference Bridge
•	Enhanced Call Management / Forwarding 
•	Caller ID & Caller ID Blocking
•	3-Way Calling
•	Call Waiting
•	Do Not Disturb
•	NEW! Shared company contacts – create and share business contacts between your company accounts to ensure you never miss an opportunity! Easily sort and find your company’s contacts through our easy to use filter tool, allowing you to easily manage between personal and business calls.

Use magicJack for BUSINESS on devices running iOS14 or higher. 
This application requires users to have a magicJack for Business account set-up. 

*Unlimited calling to numbers within the United States and Canada and other services provided by magicJack for BUSINESS™ are based on normal, non-excessive use. A combination of factors is used to determine excessive use, including but not limited to the relative use when compared to the average magicJack for BUSINESS™ user, the number of unique numbers called, calls forwarded, minutes used and other factors. Unlimited calling does not include calls to Alaska or the Yukon and Northwest Territories of Canada or calls to non-8YY calling card, platform, conference or chat lines, for which additional fees will apply. Porting an existing phone number is subject to an additional fee, and may not be available for all numbers. Annual and monthly fees quoted do not include purchase of telephone equipment and related products or shipping, regulatory fees and taxes as applicable. Subject to our Terms of Service and all applicable terms and conditions, laws and regulations, located https://www.magicjackforbusiness.com/terms/.

apps.title: Laundry Tycoon - Business Sim
apps.description:
Looking for tycoon games? Laundry Tycoon – Business Sim is a business simulator game where you run a laundry business. You make money on washing and cleaning clothes. But to succeed you need to prove yourself as a manager! Grow your business fast to become a business tycoon.

This business simulator game is really easy to play. You are a laundry manager. Simply get dirty clothes from customers and put it in the washing machine. Then take the clean clothes and give it back to get paid. The more clothes you wash the more money you get.

At first, you run the laundry by yourself. But then you need help to cope with the influx of customers and their dirty clothes. Thus, you have to do more than in most of the other cleaning games. You need to manage people for success! Get a HR Specialist to hire first workers. This will help you get rid of your laundry routine and focus on your business. Sometimes you will need to contact the HR department to hire new employees and improve your staff’s hard skills.

Indeed, don’t forget to improve your hero skills! Go to the manager desk to increase your speed and upgrade your hero to do the laundry faster. Also, upgrade the speed of the washing machines. Wash more clothes to earn more. Money will help to grow faster and build your own laundry empire.

WHAT ELSE?

- Level up your business. 
Enlarge your laundry space and buy more washing machines. Build your successful business and leave your competitors behind.

- Get CEO. 
Hire CEO to work with customers and get you rid of the routine. Instead, focus on marketing and profits. Invest more money in advertising to attract more customers. Improve your service quality. This will allow you to rise prices and to become a business tycoon.

- Serve VIP customers. 
Wanna make even more money? Wash clothes for VIPs and get gold for your work. The richer men you attract the faster your dream will come true!

Download Laundry Tycoon – Business Sim, pump your laundry business up and become a millionaire tycoon!

apps.title: ABBYY Business Card Reader Pro
apps.description:
ABBYY Business Card Reader Pro –The World’s Fastest Business Card Scanner & Contact Management App for iPhone and iPad! 

Recommended by The New York Times, CNN, The Telegraph, Computer Business Review, Macworld. 
Winner of the RISING STAR Award in the Mobile Star Awards 

ABBYY Business Card Reader Pro easily & simply captures & stores contact from business cards in 25 languages to your iPhone and iPad. The recognized data can be saved in either your device contacts or the app digital storage.

KEY FEATURES
• QUICK AND ACCURATE SCANNING
ABBYYs optical character recognition technology provides quick & accurate recognition of all contact information: names, organizations, phone numbers, e-mail addresses, etc. 	 
• AUTO-CLICK PHOTO FEATURE
Automatically focuses on the business card, detects its edges, crops any extraneous background & captures an image of the card all by itself. 
• EASY CHECK OF RECOGNIZED DATA
The app highlights “unusual” characters with blue color and displays the original image so that you can quickly confirm the output of the app.
• APPLE WATCH APP. You won’t need to reach for your iPhone or iPad to remember somebody’s name. View contacts and make phone calls right from BCR on your Apple Watch! 
• AUTOMATIC NORMALIZATION OF PHONE AND EXTENTION NUMBERS
BCR will automatically put in all the missing parts so that you can reach the contact even if the country code was omitted in print. 
• AUTOCOMPLETION OF ADDRESSES
BCR corrects any typos and fills in the missing address fields so you can easily find it on the map.
• MANUAL BACKUPS. Manual backups to archive and restore to another device.
• Export contacts to Salesforce Leads (premium account required). BCR can export business cards to Enterprise, Unlimited, and Performance Editions of SF license.  Professional Edition does not allow BCR export. 
• Set up voice commands in Siri Shortcuts app to open business cards by voicing the name of the owner.
• Spotlight Search to find business cards from BCR 
• Export business cards to MS Excel in .CSV format.
• Smart Facebook and LinkedIn search: connect social media account to the business card and auto upload photo of contact from Facebook.
• Search in iPhone Maps for the address of your contacts.
• Exchange digitally and forward recognized contacts via e-mail as VCard or JPEG files or via SMS as a plain text.
• Share your contacts using QR code.
• Support 25 languages including recognition of multilingual cards.
- French
- German
- Greek
- Japanese
- Indonesian
- Italian
- Korean
- Norwegian (both Bokmal and Nynorsk)
- Polish
- Portuguese (Portugal)
- Portuguese (Brazil)
- Russian
- Spanish
- Swedish
- Turkish
- Ukrainian


Read us:
abbyy.com/blog/mobile
Facebook.com/ABBYYsoft
Twitter @ABBYY_Software
YouTube.com/ABBYYvideos

Alibaba.com is one of the world’s leading B2B ecommerce marketplaces. Our app allows you to source products from global suppliers, all from the convenience of your mobile device.

Our Trade Assurance service protects your orders and payments on the platform, letting you purchase securely and conveniently with extended support.

Customizable products
Meet suppliers with years of customization and order fulfillment experience for sellers on Amazon, eBay, Wish, Etsy, Mercari, Lazada, and more.

Easy sourcing
Discover millions of ready-to-ship products in every industry category. Tell suppliers what you need and get quotes quickly with Request for Quotation services.

Fast shipping

Popular categories and trade shows
Source a wide range of popular items – from trending consumer goods to raw materials – and join our annual trade shows for niche product highlights and discounts.

Quality control

apps.title: National Business League
apps.description:
The National Business League (NBL) is the oldest and largest African American trade association in the world, founded by the legendary Booker T. Washington on August 23, 1900 with access to more than 2.9 million Black-owned businesses throughout the word. 

The NBL has evolved into the digital economy with the introduction of its cutting-edge mobile app platform. 

Benefits: 

- B2B and C2B networking 
- Education and training 
- Events and programs 
- Marketplace for resources and support 
- News updates 

Features:

- Access to business directory 
- Event registration, pay and promote 
- Instant updates 
- Member profiles 
- Push notifications

The article on out-of-the-box marketing techniques was particularly insightful and created some new trains of thought that I hadn’t considered up to this point with regard to my marketing and branding.  Really glad I subscribed. - mrmogul

apps.title: Allo: AI Second Business Phone
apps.description:
Your Business, Simplified: The All-in-One Phone System for Professionals

Discover the ultimate business phone system designed to revolutionize how you connect, communicate, and grow. Whether you’re a craftsperson, a solo entrepreneur, or managing a team, our app combines cutting-edge AI capabilities with seamless integrations to deliver an unmatched communication experience. Say goodbye to outdated systems and hello to streamlined workflows with features that cater to every aspect of your business.

Why Choose Our Business Phone System?

Elevate your communication game with a solution that outshines traditional platforms:
• More than just a VoIP system, it’s your comprehensive business assistant.
• AI-driven tools, advanced call handling, and intuitive design.
• Save time, stay organized, and impress clients effortlessly.

Key Features and Benefits

Before the Call: Screening and Identification
• Block spam with our spam call blocker to ensure only relevant calls come through. 
• Identify unknown callers with real-time intelligence. 
• Choose a second phone number (and the country code of your choice), port your existing number, or forward calls to our system to enjoy all the features.

During the Call: Handling and Recording
• Make and receive calls over Wi-Fi, 5G, or VoIP, ensuring clear quality. 
• Use our call recorder to automatically save conversations for compliance and review. 
• Manage calls seamlessly with transfers, simultaneous calls, and categorization.

After the Call: Insights and Integration
• Automatically transcribe calls and send transcripts to your inbox or CRM.
• Summarize key points and extract actionable insights. 
• Sync call details with CRMs like Shopify, HubSpot, and more to keep your team aligned.

Call Flow: Smarter Call Management
• Qualify callers with the AI-powered gatekeeper to identify their needs before answering.
• Set up a customizable IVR (Interactive Voice Response) system with menus (e.g., "Press 1 for Sales"). 
• Direct calls to voicemail, a live agent, or your AI receptionist for 24/7 availability. 
• Set business hours and enable busy modes to maintain work-life balance.

AI & Automation
• Use an AI voice assistant to handle calls, take messages, and route inquiries. 
• Automatically summarize calls, extract key details, and send transcripts to your inbox. 
• Create professional greetings with AI-generated voice and music options.

Customization
• Customize your workspace with visual options for call interfaces and dashboards. 
• Create unique greetings and voicemail messages to reinforce your brand.

Accessibility
• Access the app on multiple devices.
• Manage calls and messages from anywhere with a unified platform.

How We’re Different

Our solution offers:
• Spam call blocker to enhance productivity. 
• Automatic call recording and transcription to focus on conversations. 
• AI receptionist and customizable IVR menus for 24/7 availability. 
• Deep CRM integrations for actionable insights. 
• Effortless call organization by grouping calls by contact and category.

Designed for Growing Businesses
• Whether you need a 2nd phone number for your side hustle or a fully-fledged business phone system, our app scales with you.
• From startups to established enterprises, streamline communication and deliver exceptional customer experiences.

Get Started Today
• Choose a second phone number, use forwarding, or port your existing number seamlessly to maintain your professional presence.
• Download now and discover how easy it is to manage your business calls and messages in one place.
• Take control of your business communication today. Your team—and your clients—will thank you.

Note: A paid subscription is required to access all features. Pricing details are available within the app.

https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/

apps.title: Qonto - Business Finance App
apps.description:
Qonto makes day-to-day banking easier for SMEs and freelancers, thanks to an online business account combined with invoicing, bookkeeping and spend management tools. With an innovative product, highly responsive 24/7 customer service and clear pricing, Qonto has become the European leader in its category.

Master your daily finances with a powerful business account
	•	Local IBANS
	•	Payment cards: spend up to €200,000/month. No hidden costs. Pay online or in-store, at home and abroad: whatever the situation, our range of free and premium corporate cards included in your subscription has got you covered.
	•	Transfers: flexible payment methods - from instant SEPA to speedy international transfers - so you can pay and get paid faster.
	•	Get paid anywhere: accept payments in-store, on the move with Tap to Pay on iPhone, or online with Payment links. Enjoy faster access to funds with zero friction.
	•	Transactions: unlimited history and real-time notifications.
	•	Financing: simplified access to integrated financing options: apply in minutes for our partners financing deals or ease your supplier payments with our in-house financing offer, Pay later.

Unchain your growth with a suite of financial tools
	•	Invoice management: centralize invoices & receipts in one place; get paid fast and pay your suppliers even faster.
	•	Spend management: control team spending with budgets, automatic receipt collection & tailored access.
	•	Bookkeeping: collaborate seamlessly with your accountant by connecting them to our suite of tools; get a full, real-time cash flow overview.
	•	Cash flow management: track the journey of every euro, forecast cash gaps in the weeks ahead, and see VAT updates in real time; let your unified dashboard translate scattered financial data into an actionable business roadmap.

Follow Qonto for news and company updates.

See what our customers have to say about us at https://www.trustpilot.com/review/qonto.com

Olinda Head Office is registered at 18 Rue De Navarin, 75009, Paris, France.

apps.title: Gusto Mobile
apps.description:
Gusto simplifies payroll, paycheck management, time tracking, and savings for small businesses—making it easier to manage tasks on the go with powerful tools for both employees and employers.

For business owners and payroll administrators:

Payroll: Easily run regular or off-cycle payroll on the go.
Time: Review and approve your team's hours and time off.
Team: View and manage critical team information in one place.
Onboarding: Add and onboard employees directly from the app.
Notifications: Set up notifications and permissions to suit your business.

For employees:

Paychecks: Easily manage paychecks and route money to different bank accounts.
Early Pay: Receive paychecks up to 2 days early¹ and access advances between paydays with Gusto Wallet.²
Benefits: Manage your benefits or sign up for special offers.

• Take control of your online reputation by generating first-party reviews and responding all from one place

• Connect your social media profiles and publish content from one place

apps.title: Business India
apps.description:
Business India Magazine is a biweekly business magazine published by Business India Publications Pvt. Ltd. It is one of the leading business magazines in India, with a readership of over 1 million people.

The magazine was founded in 1974 by Arun Purie, a journalist and entrepreneur. It was originally published as a monthly magazine, but it was switched to a biweekly format in 1982.

Business India Magazine covers a wide range of business topics, including:

* Corporate news and analysis
* Industry trends and forecasts
* Financial markets and analysis
* Entrepreneurship and small business
* Management and leadership
* Technology and innovation
* Global business and economy

The magazine is known for its in-depth analysis and insightful commentary on the Indian business scene. It is also known for its coverage of emerging trends and new businesses.

Catalysing the quintessential Indian dream, the housing finance sector soars, shaping the dreams and aspirations of millions in the heart of the country’s urban hubs
GMIS 2023, ASK Automotive, Lohum Cleantech, Ram Chara n Co
 
Magazine Subscriptions are available for purchase inside this app. 

One year subscription - $26.99 (automatically renewed until canceled)

Your subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. 

Your iTunes account will automatically be charged at the same price for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period unless you change your subscription preferences in your account settings. 

You can manage your subscriptions through your account settings after purchase on your device. 

No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during active subscription period.

Please visit http://www.magzter.com/ns/privacy-policy.html for our Privacy Policy and http://www.magzter.com/ns/terms_condition.html  for our Terms & Conditions

• Wabi provides clean, dedicated phone numbers guaranteed to work with WhatsApp Business!

Why Wabi?
• Not all numbers are compatible with WhatsApp. Many numbers are blocked from using WhatsApp Business, especially from other virtual number providers!
• Wabi provides clean, dedicated phone numbers guaranteed to work with WhatsApp Business!
• Forget about ordering another SIM and device, installing a landline or any other hassle! Get a number in a click of a button!
• Wabi provides numbers from 60+ countries, but if there's no local phone number available for your country you may still get a US number or any other number and activate a WhatsApp account!

What is Whatsapp Business?
WhatsApp Business is another WhatsApp app intended to be used by business owners to chat with their customers, providing additional features specifically designed for businesses.

Why Whatsapp Business?
• Talk to your customers using their favorite chat app!
• Have complete separation of your personal chats, and your business customers and leads.
• Set your business profile, including working hours and business location, for your customers to see.
• Auto-reply message when off work hours.
• Auto greeting message for when new customers first message you.
• Labeling of customers (New Customer, Pending Payment, etc.).

How to use
1. Use Wabi to get a phone number compatible with Whatsapp Business.
2. Use the number to create a business account at Whatsapp Business.
3. Advertise it so your customers may reach you!
4. (Optional) Got a website? Add our free "Click To Chat" button, and allow your visitors to contact you via WhatsApp! (Go to our website for more information)

apps.title: Chatwork - Business Chat App
apps.description:
Let Chatwork streamline your business.
Chatwork is a free business chat tool that streamlines email, phone calls, meetings, visits, and other internal communication.
Chatwork can be used for telework, remote work, and task management as well.
It has been adopted in a number of industries and companies, including KDDI Corporation, GREE, Inc., and Kyoto University.

▼ Main features
Chat
Communicate within the company more quickly than by email and improve productivity.

Task management
Tasks can be managed separately from chat communications, preventing oversights and omissions.

Video calling/voice calling
Video calling and voice calling accommodate multiple users, making telework and remote work more trouble-free.

File sharing
Photo and video files taken on mobile devices can be easily shared.

Push notifications
Push notifications let the content of messages be viewed so important messages are seen quickly.

Security
A chat tool that has obtained certification under the international ISMS standard, Chatwork can be used with confidence even for important work.

Thank you for your continued support.

apps.title: SendHub - Business SMS
apps.description:
SendHub makes business SMS fast, simple, and effective. We offer an all-in-one online messaging solution to meet the SMS needs of businesses of all sizes.

A SendHub account is required to use this app. 

SendHub does not support international usage and is only available for use in the US and Canada.
To sign up for a SendHub account visit SendHub online.
Existing customers, download the app and login to use.

Think of SendHub as Gmail+Asana for SMS.

We offer businesses of all types the ability to communicate via SMS to their customers, on-the-go workers, and contact of all kinds.

Easy Setup

Get up and running in minutes without any additional hardware or developer’s help.
	
Complete Solution

Manage all inbound and outbound messages to your dedicated business line from an online dashboard.

Work Efficiently

Save time and be more productive with powerful features designed to streamline 
processes across teams and departments

Features and services include:
 • Dedicated text enabled business phone number
 • Unified Messaging Inbox
 • Shortcode (on select plans)
 • Group Messages
 • Inbound MMS 
 • Voicemail transcription
 • File attachments
 • Message archives
 • Real time usage analytics
 • Bulk message thread operations
 • Auto responder
 • Message forwarding
 • Message scheduling

As seen in: TechCrunch, GigaOM, PC Magazine, Mashable, INC Magazine, Entrepreneur,Forbes, MarketWatch, & VentureBeat.

Ad Free, iOS 8 + US, Canada ONLY. 

Need to contact us?
Support: support@sendhub.com or in the app under "Settings>Help".
Twitter: @SendHub
Facebook: www.facebook.com/SendHub

raw_data.releaseNotes:
What’s New
=>  You can now send SMS and MMS messages to email threads directly from the app.
=>  When messaging an email thread, certain options (Call, Schedule Message, Merge Field, Template) are hidden for clarity.
=>  For threads with multiple contacts, tapping the thread title now shows all participants. Blocked contacts are marked with a blocked icon and displayed in grey colour.
=> Auto Reply has been enhanced to support both email and contact updates.

We’re always working to make the app better — thanks for using it!

apps.title: Xero Accounting for business
apps.description:
With Xero Accounting, keep track of cash flow, view income, manage expenses, and create invoices on the go. Xero Accounting app is a business tracking app, ideal for small business owners, managers and landlords. The app acts as a companion to your Xero account, helping you stay productive and keep an eye on your business’ financial health, when and where it suits you. Managing your business finances, invoices, cash flow, income and expenses, has never been so easy. 

~

Features:

MANAGE INVOICING ON THE GO
• Raise & send quotes for faster client approval & get started on the job sooner
• Reduce the time it takes to get paid by raising & sending invoices from your device as soon as the job is completed
• Create an invoice in a few simple steps, & send directly to clients via email, text message or other apps
• Void invoices easily from your phone
• Easily keep track of unpaid invoices, to see who owe's you what - and even track the status of an invoice, seeing if it has been viewed by clients

ACCEPT CONTACTLESS PAYMENTS RIGHT ON YOUR iPhone
(currently only available in the U.S, Australia, the U.K, New Zealand & Canada)
• Expand where you do business. Accept in-person, contactless payments right on your iPhone, so you can reach new customers & take payments on the go
• Accept contactless payments from physical debit/credit cards, Apple Pay & other digital wallets. So there’s no need for additional hardware such as card readers or terminals
• Privacy & security of iPhone built in. Apple doesn’t store card numbers or PIN information on your iPhone or Apple servers, so merchants & customers can rest assured that their data stays theirs
• Tap to Pay on in the Xero Accounting App is free to set up, with no ongoing or monthly subscription fees. Stripe transactions fees still apply
• Save time, improve cash flow & focus on growing your business

KEEP TRACK OF CASH FLOW
• View summaries of outstanding bills & invoices to see what’s owed
• Monitor your flexible profit & loss report which can be viewed on a cash or accrual basis & helps you keep your finger on your business’ financial health
• Drill down profit & loss reports, to help understand your business as well as answer questions on sales & spending
• (NEW) Quickly & easily create bills by capturing photos or selecting files from your mobile device, with our new automatic bill uploader with AI

MANAGE SPEND
• Record spend as soon as it happens to reduce office admin & time spent looking for lost receipts

RECONCILE FROM ANYWHERE
• Good bookkeeping habits have been made easy - Smart matches, rules & suggestions makes reconciling your business transactions easy, from anywhere with a few simple clicks
• Filter bank statement lines to optimise your unique workflow, leading to faster reconciliation
• New sort & search tools to make it easier to view business transactions & streamline the reconciliation process

MANAGE CUSTOMER & SUPPLIER INFORMATION
• Have vital contact information in the palm of your hand so you can do business from wherever you are
• Get a view of how much is owed and quickly add notes so you can build better business relationships

~

XERO ACCOUNTING APP IS POWERED BY XERO
Xero is a global small business platform that connects your small business to accountants, bookkeepers, banks & apps. We’re proud to be helping over 3 million+ subscribers worldwide and your business could be next
 
To contact support, visit us at https://central.xero.com/, raise a ticket, book a call & someone will reach out to you
Got product & feature ideas for the Xero Accounting App? Visit https://productideas.xero.com/

You're in good hands with Xero. We're rated GREAT on Trustpilot (4/5) with 10K+ customer reviews (as of 23/09/2025)

Downloading & accessing the Xero Accounting mobile app is subject to the acceptance of Apple's Standard EULA https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/
More terms apply if you use Xero's services, see https://www.xero.com/legal/terms/

apps.title: Everlance: Mileage Tracker
apps.description:
"A driver’s co-pilot" - The New York Times

Trusted by over 4 million drivers, freelancers, and small business owners.
Everlance automatically tracks your miles, captures expenses, and uncovers tax deductions.
Save thousands a year on average in taxes and reimbursements.
Partners include DoorDash, Lyft, Thumbtack, Wag!, Shipt, Realtor associations, and more

Whether you’re delivering food, managing clients, or running your own business, Everlance is your companion on the road, keeping your records organized, your taxes simple, and your reimbursements accurate.

Log every trip automatically, connect your bank or card to capture expenses, uncover hidden savings with Deduction Finder, generate IRS-ready reports, and even file your 1099 taxes in-app. With $1M audit protection in Professional, you’re covered on every drive.

▶ WHY EVERLANCE

Most mileage apps stop at tracking trips. Everlance goes further, giving you peace of mind that every mile and every expense is accounted for. From fuel and tolls to supplies and parking, you’ll always be tax-ready without the stress.

→ "Everlance is easier and more intuitive than many other mileage trackers. The app syncs with your phone’s GPS and tracks your mileage for you automatically. From there, you can easily label trips as personal or work-related" -  U.S. Chamber of Commerce

▶ WHAT YOU GET

• Automatic GPS mileage tracking in the background
• Easy expense capture by linking your card or snapping receipts
• Deduction Finder to uncover extra write-offs instantly
• IRS-compliant reports for taxes or reimbursements
• Optional 1099 tax filing and $1M Audit Protection in Professional

→ "What makes it especially great for the self-employed is its assistance in managing taxes. Its deduction finder even scans expenses to see if there’s anything else you can file as a tax deduction" - Wired Magazine

▶ WHY IT MATTERS

Every mile you drive for work is money back in your pocket. For 2025, the IRS rate is 70 cents per mile, that’s $700 for every 1,000 miles. Missing even a few trips could mean hundreds or thousands lost at tax time.

Everlance makes sure nothing slips through the cracks. With every mile logged, every receipt stored, and every deduction captured, your records are always complete and ready for tax season.

→ "If you operate a solo business, Everlance could become your new favorite app" - The College Investor

▶ WHO IT'S FOR

If you drive your own vehicle for work or charity, Everlance was built for you.

• Delivery & rideshare drivers (DoorDash, Uber, Lyft, Instacart, Shipt)
• Freelancers and contractors juggling multiple clients
• Real estate agents and field sales reps
• Small business owners looking for an all-in-one tax tool
• Employees getting reimbursed for mileage
• Nonprofit volunteers tracking charitable miles

→ "Everlance is by far the best option I’ve found, combining a simple, attractive interface with a price that’s impossible to beat. I’ve been using Everlance for the past several months, and it has earned a permanent spot on my phone" -  CNET

▶ PLANS TO FIT YOUR NEEDS

Download Everlance for free and eliminate the headache of mileage and expense tracking.

• Basic (Free, no credit card required): Manual mileage tracking, 30 automatic trips per month, and reports
• Starter: Unlimited automatic mileage tracking, smart trip classification, IRS-compliant reports
• Professional: Everything in Starter plus expense tracking, Deduction Finder, 1099 tax filing, and $1M Audit Protection

Every plan comes with a free 7-day trial so you can experience everything before you commit.

---
Customer support is available in English, Spanish, and French. Contact us at support@everlance.com.

Privacy Policy: https://www.everlance.com/privacy
Terms of Service: https://www.everlance.com/terms-of-service
Terms of Use (EULA): https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/

Download Everlance today for free and enjoy more profit & peace of mind on the road ahead.

raw_data.releaseNotes:
In 5.4.1, we made some updates to prepare for tax season 2026. Yup. Tax season, 2026. Kinda crazy right?...but it's Q4..and not only is it Q4..but it's already half way through October. Meaning tax season is almost here. So we're preparing for you to prepare. 

If you didn't track your miles and expenses throughout the year, check out our deduction finder..it's pretty great, and can scan your expenses over the last 12 months looking for deductions. 

and if you like how we're doing, leave us a review!

Cheers!

apps.title: Relay | Business Banking
apps.description:
Relay is online business banking that puts small business owners in complete control of their cash flow.

What Relay offers:

• 20 checking accounts to earmark cash for operations, payroll, taxes and more
• Multiple debit and credit cards—with built-in spend policies—to meticulously organize spending by team or project
• 1.5% cash back* on all credit card purchases, and savings accounts with up to 3.00% APY** to help you grow reserves
• All the payment types you could need—including ACH transfers, wires and checks (yes, including paper checks!)
• Automations—like maximum-balance transfer rules—that make money move for you so can focus on running your business

Plus, each business is insured up to $3M for funds on deposit via Thread Bank, Member FDIC.***   


Learn more at relayfi.com.





Relay is a financial technology company, not a bank. Banking services are provided through Thread Bank, Member FDIC. The Relay Visa® Debit Card is issued by Thread Bank, Member FDIC, pursuant to a license from Visa U.S.A. Inc. and may be used everywhere Visa® cards are accepted. The Relay Visa® Credit Card is issued by Thread Bank, Member FDIC, pursuant to a license from Visa U.S.A. Inc. and may be used everywhere Visa credit cards are accepted.

*Terms and conditions apply to the cash back rewards program. Cash back will be credited to your Relay checking account at the end of your 30-day billing cycle. ATM transactions, the purchase of money orders or cash equivalents made with your Relay Visa® Credit Card are not eligible for cash back. Please refer to https://relayfi.com/visa-signature-rewards-program-terms for more details.

**The interest rates and annual percentage yield on your account are accurate as of 9/18/2024 and are variable and subject to change based on the target range of the Federal Funds rate. APY will vary between 1.00%-3.00% depending on the balances held. Earn 1.00% APY on savings balances of less than $50,000, 1.50% APY on savings between $50,000 and $250,000, 2.00% APY on savings balances between $250,000 and $1,000,000 and 3.00% APY on savings balances of more than $1,000,000. There are no minimum balances or minimum deposits required to earn interest on your account.

***Your deposits qualify for up to $3,000,000 in FDIC insurance coverage when placed at program banks in Thread Bank, Member FDIC’s deposit sweep program. Your deposits at each program bank become eligible for FDIC insurance up to $250,000, inclusive of any other deposits you may already hold at the bank in the same ownership capacity. You can access the terms and conditions of the sweep program at https://go.thread.bank/sweepdisclosure and a list of program banks at https://go.thread.bank/programbanks. Please contact customerservice@thread.bank with questions regarding the sweep program.

apps.title: IndiaMART: Buy & Sell Products
apps.description:
Best Business App Award 2017
 
IndiaMART: Search for Products, Buyers, Sellers, Resellers, Wholesalers, Manufacturers & Retailers
 
With the IndiaMART App, millions of buyers & sellers can connect with each other to fulfil their business requirements. Browse through India's largest online B2B marketplace & explore the widest range of products & services. Expand your business' visibility to reach more than 8 crores+ Buyers or 55 lakhs+ genuine suppliers for your sourcing requirements. IndiaMART brings together leading manufacturers, verified sellers, resellers, wholesalers & retailers looking for an easy way to widen their reach manifold.
 
The IndiaMART App comes loaded with features that make it easy to connect to & find new online shopping opportunities anytime, anywhere.

IndiaMART Crowned Awards :
 
1. Manthan Award
2. Red Herring Award
3. Emerging India Award
 
Get in touch with sellers, resellers, retailers & wholesalers from our top selling online shopping categories :
 
Electronics & Electrical Goods & Services
Building & Construction Material
Industrial Plants & Machinery
Apparel Clothing & Garments
And Thousands More…
 
Why switch to IndiaMART App ?
 
For Buyers :
 
1. Search for Products & Services 24x7, Send Enquiries & Post your Requirements. Get instant alerts & stay updated no matter where you are.
2. Post Requirements & Send Enquiries in Offline Mode as well.
3. Compare Quotes from multiple suppliers & get best prices. 
4. Pay instantly and do business securely using Pay with IndiaMART.
5. Buy from sellers near you - Search in your area with the help of Geo-Location.
6. Get detailed information about products & chat with sellers on the go. Discuss your requirement in detail, negotiate the price & buy from India's most trusted suppliers.
7. Mark your preferred products as "My Favourites" to check them out later.
 
 
For Sellers :
 
1. Purchase Buy Leads on the go - Connect to potential customers instantly & discover new opportunities to sell online.
2. Review & Respond to enquiries anytime, anywhere, categorise them into multiple folders. Sell to interested customers easily. 
3. Receive Payments hassle-free through Pay with IndiaMART.
4. Add reminders & notes to increase lead conversion. Add prices to your catalog easily.
5. Search Buy Leads by Product Name & increase your chances of conversion.
6. Never miss an opportunity to grow sales. Receive instant Buyleads & Enquiry notifications. 
7. Upload & Download PDF, Product Images, Documents in Enquiry chat for better communication.
 
The IndiaMART App also supports exclusive features for individual accounts, as well as detailed catalog listing view, as per categories & sub-categories, thus facilitating on-the-go deals for them. Whether you are an importer or exporter, seller or reseller, manufacturer, wholesaler or a SME, with the help of IndiaMART App, you can buy & sell across the globe with utmost ease. Get instant buy leads & sell with high rates of conversion. Join over 47 lakh+ suppliers who are already a part of IndiaMART.
 
You say, we hear :

For any queries, you can call our dedicated customer care helpline number 09696969696 or write to us at AppCare@indiamart.com
