apps.title: Pages
apps.description:
Pages is the most beautiful word processor you’ve ever seen on a mobile device. Start with an Apple-designed template to instantly create gorgeous reports, digital books, resumes, posters, and more. Or use a blank document and create your own design. Easily add images, movies, audio, tables, charts, and shapes. You can even draw and annotate using Apple Pencil on supported devices, or use your finger. Pages has been designed exclusively for iPad and iPhone.

Draw and annotate using Apple Pencil or your finger
• Easily add drawings with pen, pencil, crayon, and fill tools, then animate them and watch them come to life
• Use Smart Annotation to add comments and marks that stay anchored to their associated text
• Convert your handwritten words to typed text with Scribble and Apple Pencil

Collaborate with others at the same time
• With real-time collaboration, your whole team can work together on a document at the same time on Mac, iPad, iPhone, and even on a PC
• Share your document publicly or with specific people, see who’s currently in the document with you, and view other people’s cursors to follow their edits
• See a list of recent changes in collaborative documents, including when people join, comment, and make edits
• Available for documents stored in iCloud or in Box

Get started quickly
• Choose from over 90 Apple-designed templates to instantly create beautiful reports, digital books, resumes, cards, posters, and more
• Use Screen View on iPhone to automatically display text, images, and other elements in a continuous flow optimized to fit your screen so documents are even easier to read and edit
• Get quick access to shapes, media, tables, charts, and sharing options
• Import and edit Microsoft Word and text files
• Quickly open password-protected documents using Touch ID or Face ID on supported devices

Create beautiful documents
• Format your document with gorgeous styles, fonts, and textures
• Enhance your document with a library of over 700 editable shapes
• Easily add images, video, and audio
• Add an image gallery to view a collection of photos on the same page
• Create interactive EPUB books that can be shared with others or published to Apple Books for download or purchase

Advanced tools
• Use the table of contents view to easily navigate your document or book
• Add comments and join threaded conversations
• Turn on change tracking to mark up a document as you edit it
• Add bookmarks to easily link from one part of your document to another
• View pages side by side as you work
• Turn on facing pages to format your document as two-page spreads
• Create page templates to keep the design consistent across your page layout document
• Add linked text boxes so text easily flows from one place to another
• Create footnotes and endnotes and view character, word, and paragraph counts
• Add elegant mathematical equations using LaTeX or MathML notation

apps.title: Melio Business Payments
apps.description:
Melio is the accounts payable and receivable platform that gives growing businesses the control, visibility, and flexibility they need to thrive. Our mobile app puts all that power right in your pocket.

Handle your incoming and outgoing payments confidently from anywhere with Melio's streamlined mobile experience. Scan bills on the go, approve team payments with a swipe, and stay on top of your cash flow—no desk required.

WITH THE MELIO APP YOU CAN:
Pay vendors fast and your way—ACH, card, or check—with just a few taps
Easily add vendors directly from your contacts
Track every payment with real-time notifications
Capture and upload bills instantly with your camera
Approve your payments on the move

TAKE CONTROL OF YOUR FINANCES 
Smart payment scheduling, approval workflows, and complete visibility put you in the driver's seat. Keep cash working for your business by choosing exactly when and how money moves.

STREAMLINE YOUR OPERATIONS 
Process multiple bills at once, add vendors straight from your contacts, and automate your financial workflows. Connect with your accounting software for seamless reconciliation that saves hours of manual work.

OPTIMIZE YOUR CASH FLOW 
Stay in control with flexible payment options. Pay by credit card (even to vendors who don't accept cards—we can send them an ACH or check for you), schedule payments strategically, or use Fast ACH to time your cash flow perfectly.

YOUR VENDORS, YOUR TERMS 
Your vendors get paid their way, without needing to sign up. You maintain control over timing and payment methods, creating a win-win for everyone.
Melio is trusted by top financial institutions and was named to the 2024 Forbes Fintech 50 list, recognizing the most innovative private financial technology companies. We're also proud to be named one of CNBC's top 250 fintech companies this year.

apps.title: Onoff Business
apps.description:
With Onoff Business, you don't need a second phone anymore, you have a number in the cloud instead of a physical SIM card, and everything happens on an app!
 
Manage all your business communications on a single phone with the Onoff Business app. Download the app and start making calls instantly!

In order to be able to use this mobile application, your company needs to have an
active Onoff Business account. If you don't, please visit https://www.onoffbusiness.com/en/

If your enterprise has shared with you the access to your Onoff Business account, download the app now and you can instantly start making calls!

Onoff Business, the ARCEP-recognised French telecommunications operator, allows enterprises to provide professional mobile numbers to their employees through a simple and intuitive web platform. Employees then just need to download the Onoff Business application on their phones. The Onoff Business numbers support incoming & outgoing calls as well as SMS/MMS as a regular phone number but without needing to have another phone or a second SIM card. A visual voicemail is included. The application is accessible from any smartphone or tablet.

Need a second number for personal usage? You can download the original Onoff
app.

Do not hesitate to share your feedback and comments at support@onoffbusiness.com

General conditions: https://www.onoffbusiness.com/en/terms-conditions/

apps.title: Expensify - Travel & Expense
apps.description:
Expensify helps more than 15 million people around the world track expenses, reimburse employees, manage corporate cards, send invoices, pay bills, and book travel. All at the speed of chat.

Expensify is built for:

* Self-employed: Track and categorize expenses for budgeting or tax purposes. Scan receipts, log distance, or just type in an amount. Send invoices to clients and chat with them in the same place.
* Small business owners: Say goodbye to spreadsheets. Keep employees happy with easy expense management and quick reimbursements. Clear up any questions in a chat on the expense or report level. Sync with QuickBooks Online, Xero, and more.
* Growing teams: Scale up your spend management with the Expensify corporate card, built-in travel booking and trip chat rooms, and multi-level approval workflows. Sync with Sage Intacct, NetSuite, and more.
* Enterprise companies: Reimburse employees in every country. Manage expenses in every currency. Import transactions from every type of corporate or personal card.

Key features:

* Chat: Keep your money moving with realtime chat built into every type of transaction.
* Receipt scanning: Snap a picture of any receipt and SmartScan extracts the details.
* Distance tracking: Log miles or kilometers on a beautiful map, at custom rates.
* Manual expenses: No receipt? Just type in an amount. Still better than a spreadsheet.
* Categorization: Code your expenses once and then we’ll learn to do it for you.
* Submissions: Expenses auto-submit in realtime, or you can set a custom cadence.
* Approvals: Add one or more expense approvers to your workflow for more control.
* Expense chat: Questions about an expense? Ask and approve in the same place.
* Reimbursements: Pay back your employees at home or around the world.
* Expensify Card: Get up to 2% cash back on all US purchases and save on your bill.
* Corporate cards: Give your team the Expensify Card or import your own.
* Invoices: Send, view, discuss, and pay invoices in a chat. No more app + email combos.
* Travel: Book flights, hotels, and rental cars right in the app. T&E at its finest.
* Trip rooms: A chat room for every trip to organize expenses and answer questions.
* Accounting: Sync with QuickBooks, Xero, Sage Intacct, NetSuite, and more.
* Security: 2FA, PCI-DSS Level 1, SOC1 and SOC2 Type II Certified.
* Other integrations: Uber, Lyft, Delta, ADP, Gusto, Zenefits, Workday, and more.

Run your back office at the speed of chat. Download Expensify today.

The Expensify Visa® Commercial Card is issued by The Bancorp Bank, N.A., Member FDIC, pursuant to a license from Visa U.S.A. Inc. and may not be used at all merchants that accept Visa cards.

apps.title: Business Game - Life Simulator
apps.description:
Embark on an exhilarating journey of ambition and decision-making in "Business Life," the ultimate life simulator that puts you in control of your destiny. Start from scratch and pave your way to success in this immersive simulation game that combines elements of exchange, crypto, business, and relationship management.
Build Your Business Empire:
Construct your business from the ground up. Make strategic decisions, invest wisely, and watch your company thrive. From small ventures to multinational corporations, the power is in your hands.
Exchange and Crypto Management:
Dive into the dynamic world of exchange and crypto. Monitor market trends, make informed choices, and build your fortune by navigating the volatile yet rewarding landscape of digital assets.
Relationships Matter:
Forge meaningful connections both personally and professionally. Your relationships impact your success, so nurture them wisely. Build a network of allies, partners, and maybe even find love along the way.
Skills and Development:
Sharpen your skills to stay ahead of the competition. From leadership to technical expertise, continuous development is key to unlocking new opportunities and overcoming challenges.
Life Choices and Consequences:
Every decision you make shapes your character's journey. Be prepared to face the consequences of your choices, whether it's a lucrative business deal or a personal relationship.
Immersive Life Simulation:
Experience a realistic simulation of life's twists and turns. Navigate through ups and downs, overcome obstacles, and celebrate your triumphs as you live out your entrepreneurial dreams.
Why "Business Life"?
Engaging Gameplay: Dive into a captivating blend of strategy, simulation, and decision-making.
Endless Possibilities: Explore a vast virtual world filled with opportunities and challenges.
Realistic Business Dynamics: Learn and adapt to the ever-changing landscape of the business world.
Social Interaction: Connect with friends, compete in business challenges, and collaborate on ventures.
Unleash the entrepreneur in you – download "Business Life" now and start building the life you've always dreamed of!
Feel free to customize this description to better fit the unique aspects and features of your game.

apps.title: M-PESA for Business
apps.description:
The M-PESA for Business app is the easiest way for M-PESA merchants to transact and track M-PESA collections and disbursements.

In this initial version, merchants will be able to:

Track business growth

·        View your organization’s Money-in and Money-out trends from a performance graph. Click to see accumulated values per day.

View full Statements

·        See all transactions that were made or received in your account. Use Money-in and Money-out to filter between credits and debits.

Transact

·        Pay Customer feature allows you to send money to pay suppliers, refunds or salaries directly to their M-PESA.

·        Withdraw money allows merchants to move money collected on the till to owners’ M-PESA account, M-PESA agent or bank

·         Pay Bill and Buy Goods allows merchants to pay their suppliers directly from their M-PESA till

Manage their account

· 	Multiple account support allows you to log in to, manage and transact on multiple till numbers under the same nominated number

· 	Roll up allows you to push funds collected to the head office

raw_data.releaseNotes:
Thank you for using the M-PESA app!

We are always working on new features, improvements, and ensuring the stability of the application.

In this version, we’re changing the application font style in order to complying with the organization requirements and branding standards.

apps.title: Clover Go - Dashboard & POS
apps.description:
Clover simplifies the lives of small business owners with a tailored, all-in-one point-of-sale (POS) system that enables them to accept payments as well as run and grow their business.  Clover Go extends the power of Clover by allowing merchants to accept payments, track sales and manage their business from anywhere on their mobile device.

● Run your business from anywhere: Track sales in real-time, identify your most popular items, view employee performance, and manage your business from your mobile devices (some features require supporting service plans).
● Accept payments easily: Use Tap to Pay on iPhone to accept contactless payments without any additional hardware, or record cash payments.
● Peace of mind with built-in security: Every transaction is encrypted end-to-end to protect your customers’ data and your business.
● Get help whenever you need it: Contact us by phone or email 24/7/365, or ask us to call you from within the app (More>Help>Call me).

A Clover merchant account is required to use this app. If you don’t have a Clover merchant account, sign up for Clover at www.clover.com.

*Note that rooted or jailbroken devices are not supported due to security risks.

raw_data.releaseNotes: This release includes improvements that keep the app optimized for reliability, functionality and ease-of-use.

Use Shopify Inbox to talk with customers and sell over chat. With Shopify Inbox, you can close sales faster, build strong customer relationships, and spend less time on support all from a free business chat app.

USE CHAT TO SELL MORE AND BUILD STRONG RELATIONSHIPS


Shopify Inbox is so much more than support. In fact, 70% of Shopify Inbox conversations are with customers making a purchasing decision.

Use Shopify Inbox to:
• Save time managing customer conversations from online store chat and the Shop app
• Send products, discounts, and new orders from your Shopify store directly inside chats with just a few taps to turn more conversations into checkouts
• Send automated messages and continue chats over email so you don’t need to respond in real time
• Know when customers add or remove items from their shopping cart
• Assign chats to your staff and team to scale customer conversations


SHOP APP
Let customers contact you from the Shop app.

 -----------

FEEDBACK & SUPPORT

For 24/7 support visit the Shopify Help Center: help.shopify.com


Thank you for using Shopify Inbox on iOS. We love hearing your feedback. Please let us know what you think of Shopify Inbox by leaving a review.

apps.title: Business Card Maker!
apps.description:
A business card is the first impression of your brand. Every professional needs a business card or a visiting card. 

Here is the business card maker app that helps you to create creative business cards.

Key Features
- Insert texts like your name, company name, mobile number, email address, website, etc... 
- Select your business card from various business card designs.
- Custom Design Editor
- Save or Share business card
- Save your business time without any designer.

When you meet someone that could potentially be a great prospect or connection, don’t you want him or her to walk away with a great first impression?
A memorable business card does a lot more than just pass on an email address or phone number.

Creative business cards get shared -- continuing to market for you.

A business card is a physical object that a potential prospect leaves the encounter with. Your brand stays with them.

If you meet a prospect and exchange email addresses and phone numbers you each walk away with another contact on your mobile phone -- it ends there. If you hand over a creative business card that makes a great impression that a person is likely to show it to other people -- putting you and your brand in front of additional prospects.

Business cards show you are prepared.

The Importance of Business Cards For Professionals

1. Business cards give people the ability to follow up

2. Business cards show that you are a professional
3. Having a business card keeps one focused on the goal
4. Business cards can help make you referable
5. Luck happens when preparation meets opportunity.

In saying that make sure that you always have your business cards with you so when the opportunity comes you are already prepared and you too may get “lucky” and find success.

Business cards put a face to a business – When meeting someone new, handing them your business card (preferably with your photo on it) will help keep your business in the back of their minds. Though they may not need your product or services today, there may come a time when they do, and hopefully, they will be able to pull out your business card and call versus trying to remember your company name and searching the web.

How to create your professional business card?
- Incorporate QR codes in your business card
- Spend more on quality
- Choose the right font
- Consider professional help

If you choose to subscribe to any of the “Business Card Maker Pro” Subscriptions, the payment will be charged to your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase. any unused portion of the free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when you purchase a subscription to that publication. From that moment and further, the subscription automatically renews until auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. You may manage your subscription and turn off auto-renewal by going to your account settings after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during the active period. If you have any questions while using this app, please contact us via email at info@optimumbrew.com.

Terms of Use - https://flyerbuilder.app/terms-of-use/iosterms/?id=nx14d0
Privacy Policy - https://flyerbuilder.app/privacy-policy/iosprivacy-poster/?id=nx14d0

Please rate the app and give your feedback to help us improve and create many more unique apps for you.

apps.title: WordPress – Website Builder
apps.description:
Manage or create your WordPress blog or website right from your iOS device: create and edit posts and pages, upload your favorite photos and videos, view stats and reply to comments.

With WordPress for iOS, you have the power to publish in the palm of your hand. Draft a spontaneous haiku from the couch. Snap and post a photo on your lunch break. Respond to your latest comments, or check your stats to see what new countries today’s visitors are coming from.

WordPress for iOS is an Open Source project, which means you too can contribute to its development. Learn more at https://apps.wordpress.com/contribute/.

WordPress for iOS supports WordPress.com and self-hosted WordPress.org sites running WordPress 4.0 or higher.

Need help with the app? Visit the forums at https://wordpress.org/support/forum/mobile/ or tweet us @WordPressiOS.

View the Privacy Notice for California Users at https://automattic.com/privacy/#california-consumer-privacy-act-ccpa.

raw_data.releaseNotes:
You can now create an excerpt for your posts and get auto-suggested tags using Apple Intelligence. It’s also easier to pick your tags in Post Settings. Now that’s smart.
We made a few visual fixes for iOS in areas like the site creation flow, the media selection screen, and the Stats screen.
While we were at it, we also squashed a few bugs.
- Reader articles render properly on devices with Display Zoom enabled.
- The “Add Media” button stays visible in the media library. No more disappearing act.
- You can search in Reader Subscriptions without freezing the app.

apps.title: Coffee Inc: Business Tycoon
apps.description:
Welcome to The Coffee Inc, business simulation tycoon game!

As a founder and CEO, your role is to start up your coffee shop, manage coffee bean blends, create the best coffee products, hire and motivate the best talents, conduct effective marketing, manage financials, expand the business to multiple cities and build the biggest coffee empire!


=== Key Features ===

- Open more than two hundred coffee shops. Location! Location! Location!

- Choose your own exteriors, interiors and store equipment in order to differentiate your stores from competitors.

- Seven cities to expand your business (so as your competitors!).

- Develop the best coffee blends to uniquely stand out your products and shops.

- Set products and pricing strategies wisely to compete with neighboring coffee shops.

- Hire store employees, train/motivate/compensate them well and keep the service level high.

- Conduct store marketing as well as corporate level marketing to increase brand awareness and attract more customers.

- Very realistic income statement and balance sheet to provide detailed financial insights.

- Borrow money from the Bank if you are short on cash.

- File for IPO to increase the capital and expand your business aggressively.

- Acquire (M&A) competitors through the stock market.

- Once you get big, you can invest in real estate and other venture businesses.

- Expand your business to become an owner of professional sports team franchises.

- It's a turn-based game. Enjoy the game at your own pace, even offline. No more waiting for hours and days!

- Because we'd like you to fully enjoy the game, there are no annoying ads.

raw_data.releaseNotes:
- Added a link to Coffee Inc 2, new version of the game.
- Performance enhancement.

Stay connected to the business news that matters most to you with the new and improved Fox Business app for iOS!

The home screen has more content than ever before. Simply browse to discover the latest Fox Business stories and videos.

The “Watch” tab is your place to sit back and enjoy live and on-demand video featuring your favorite Fox Business Network personalities. You can watch Fox Business Network live*, catch up on full episodes*, or watch free, curated highlights.

The “Markets” tab gives you a snapshot of breaking market news and data - updated throughout the day.

Subscribe to our new push notifications and make sure you don’t miss a moment!

apps.title: Haystack Business Cards
apps.description:
Haystack: Your New Digital Business Card

Join the world’s #1 digital business cards platform, create a stunning digital business card, and make a great first impression!

Haystack is trusted by 8 million people across 400,000+ companies, including leading organisations such as Vodafone and the UN.

Haystack’s digital business cards improve your sales efficiency, enhance customer engagement, and reduce your environmental footprint.

Share your contact information instantly with a simple tap!

Key Features:
- Sleek design: Design and share customizable contactless business cards that make a great first impression
- Super-simple sharing: Share your card with a single tap directly from your phone’s home screen (using our smart sharing widget)
- Seamless integrations: Sync contact information with hundreds of CRM and marketing tools such as Salesforce, HubSpot, and Slack to automate contact management
- Powerful analytics: Track analytics on card usage, interactions, and more through the Admin Dashboard
- Super scalable: Perfect for enterprise teams, with experience, security and support for large global teams (our largest clients have more than 100,000 of their employees on Haystack)
- Really sustainable: 0% paper, 100% eco-friendly, and we plant a tree for every paid user (really!)

Whether you're an individual, a small business, or part of an enterprise, Haystack provides an effortless way to make lasting connections while boosting your digital marketing reach.

Download now and make the switch to smart, sustainable networking.

Revolutionize Your Professional Connections with QwikU!

Step into the future of networking with QwikU - your ultimate digital business card companion. Create a dynamic digital presence that not only elevates your brand but also builds impactful connections, effortlessly and eco-consciously.

QwikU is not just your digital business card platform; it’s a technological marvel that uses advanced AI to scan and recognize paper business cards. Effortlessly convert traditional cards into digital contacts and store them directly on your phone, merging convenience with innovation.

AI-Driven Contact Management Our intelligent AI system swiftly captures and digitizes information from physical business cards, ensuring you can preserve and organize your contacts with precision. Say hello to a clutter-free way of networking!

Customization at Your Fingertips Choose from our elegant collection of templates and craft a digital card that resonates with your brand identity. Personalize with ease, adding your logo, images, color schemes, and essential details. Incorporate interactive elements like social media links, videos, PDFs, and more for a comprehensive profile.

Seamless Sharing & Networking Distribute your card in an instant through text, email, QR codes, direct links, and social platforms. Keep your contacts neatly organized and integrate QwikU smoothly with your existing workflow tools.

Sustainable & Cost-Effective Embrace the sustainable choice with QwikU. Eliminate the need for paper cards and enjoy the flexibility of updating your details anytime, ensuring your professional image remains polished and current.

AI-powered scanning for quick digitization of business cards
Design eye-catching business cards offline
Include limitless information
Unique QR code for effortless sharing
Broad sharing capabilities across apps
Quick access with QwikU Home Widget
Save on costs and support environmental sustainability
For inquiries or suggestions, connect with us at support@qwiku.com.

apps.title: Wix - Website Builder
apps.description:
The Wix website builder app gives you the ability to design, customize and manage your website and online business from anywhere. The intuitive website maker will give you the tools you need to create and manage your business website, online store, blog and more.

Over 220 million people worldwide choose the Wix website creator and business manager to create professional online websites and manage every aspect of their business on the go. 

Whether your goal is to start a blog, build an online store, manage your business, or create a portfolio website, you can do it all using Wix’s powerful website builder from the Wix app.

Create a website with our website creator to manage and grow your brand and business:
* Create any kind of website—from a travel blog, professional portfolio or eCommerce website
* Help visitors find you online with a custom domain name
* Choose from over 900 strategically designed website templates
* Upload your own videos, images, content and blog posts
* Design a custom logo with our logo maker for your business
* Run your website on multi-cloud hosting, improve load time and ensure global coverage

Manage your business and website with the Wix website creator:
* Monitor your blog, portfolio, or eCommerce site from your phone 
* Use the website maker to build and manage your online store and blog 
* Grow your business with powerful marketing tools 
* Get dashboard features on mobile to manage your website, anywhere

Become a blogger:
* Write and share blog posts from your desktop or mobile
* Use blog designs and website templates to bring your blogging ideas to life
* Let readers share, follow and comment on your blog posts
* View blog stats and web analytics

Free tools you get when you create a website with the Wix website builder:
* Use our Business Name Generator to start your brand 
* Establish your brand image with Wix’s logo maker and edit as you wish
* Manage billings and expenses with a professional invoice generator
* Leverage Wix’s paystub generator to create employee pay stubs quickly and efficiently

Create and manage events:
* Streamline your events day of with the ticket scanner
* Manage and edit past, present, and future events
* Sell tickets online
* Scan tickets and check people in
* Send invitations, collect RSVPs and update guests

Engage with your community online:
* Chat with members and site visitors directly through your website or app
* Create groups around shared interests
* Start forums and group chats with members from the Wix Spaces app

Manage your eCommerce website on the go:
* Get notified about new orders and purchases, and manage them in real-time
* Update your products prices, colors and stock status instantly
* Use Wix analytics to follow trends in your online store
* Manage your inventory and upload product images seamlessly


Offer services and collect payments:
* Create and update services
* Take online session bookings directly from your website
* Get paid online commission-free
* Manage calendars, staff, attendance and clients from the app
* Connect pricing plans

apps.title: Og Business
apps.developer: One Global For Programming & Operating Computer Co. L.L.C
apps.description:
About Og Business

Managing business just got a whole lot easier
With user-focused engagement tools, multi-modal access and support, and a holistic view of your business health.

Now available to One Global customers, Og Business is an easy-to-use, personalized financial experience that will motivate and empower you to take smarter steps now and for a lifetime.

Og Business is designed to cover all areas of individual to empire of businesses and engage customers in a smart, reliable and compelling way.

Intuitive interface offers a user experience that will help manage risk, reduces time & costs, and reward customers with cashback. Based on self-reported and digitally captured data, Og Business provides engagement through business performance, personalized recommendations, rewards, coaching, tools, community interaction, and content that promotes healthier business lifestyles.

Streamline your business activities whether in-store, remote, delivery or Online acceptance on your website or app. Business payment activities have been combined within payment, billing, and collection:

• QR Code, SMS and in-app orders
• Order management and real-time alerts
• Branch and account management
• Tracking daily business activities against those of your coworkers
• Improve sales with cashback scheme
• Retain customers with loyalty scheme
• Accept payments in-store, web and apps
• Manage events with payment collections
• B2B and B2C marketplace with real-time settlement to your bank account

Og Business optimizes the customer experience by offering the ability to shop more often with next-sell, up-selling and cross-selling abilities.

What are the benefits of QR?
• Accept payments directly with local or an International customer
• Personalize your promotions and offers with existing customers, keeping tracks and ability to contact them.

How to use QR?
• Simply ask customers to Scan QR code from Og Money app or any QR Scanner.
• If the customer is not Og Money user then it will open a browser and they can select the payment methods whichever they find more convenient to pay with.
• You can predefine the amount by simply entering the amount and clicking on “Generate QR”. The customer will scan and pay the amount you entered.
• If customer scan the static QR without amount, then the agreed amount will be entered by the customer and the merchant will verify the payment status.

What are the benefits of Order?
• Creating and sending orders remotely on condition that the customer is an Og Money user.
• Orders through the Og Money app is much faster and safer rather than links that goes to web browser, which requires more input from the payer (Like card details and OTPs)  
• How to use Order?
• Simply by entering the amount, mobile number, description (if any) and finally clicking on “Send Order”
• The transaction will be in Pending tab and will be moved to Paid tab once the Og Money payer processed successfully the payment.

What are the benefits of Link?
• All customer can pay through the link shared with the Payment methods available locally and internationally.
• You can predefine the amount and send the link to one or multiple customers.
• You can schedule the collection that can be used by schools, institutions, installments, rental and on demand payment collection.

How to use Link?
• By entering the amount, description (if any) and clicking on “Generate Link”.
• The customer will receive the link via any channel sent through and pay the amount you entered.
• For security reason any payer should be verified by an OTP to make sure payments in safe for both for payer and merchant payee.

apps.title: First Horizon Mobile Banking
apps.description:
Now available for both Personal and Small Business customers!  The First Horizon Mobile Banking app is free to download and offers you a convenient, secure way to manage your financial life or your business on the go. The app lets you deposit a check, view your account balances, pay bills, transfer funds, create and manage budgets, track spending, and set timely alerts and notifications to keep you in the know.

Service Features

• Enable Quick Glance℠ to check balances and see recent transactions without logging in
• Set alerts and push notifications to your iPhone®, Apple Watch®, or iPad®
• Turn your debit and credit cards on or off
• Deposit checks with Mobile Deposit
• Check your account balances and view recent transactions
• Transfer funds between eligible accounts at any time
• Pay bills, add payees, see payments made, or cancel payments
• Send, Request, and Split money with family, friends, and people you know and trust with Zelle® using your personal bank account.
• Move money between all of your personal bank accounts – even ones at other banks
• Create budgets, designate savings goals, and track progress
• Find the nearest First Horizon ATM or banking center

Service Benefits

• Convenience – Bank wherever you go and at any time of the day
• Control – It’s easy to monitor your account and quickly move money, pay bills, and turn your card on or off
• Support – A dedicated mobile specialist is just a quick call away
• Security – Enjoy the highest level of protection against account fraud

How to Get Started

Simply download the app, use your Digital Banking credentials to log in, and you’re ready to begin banking on the go.

apps.title: HSBC HK Business Express
apps.developer: The Hongkong and Shanghai Banking Corporation Ltd.
apps.description:
No matter where you are amongst your busy schedule, staying on top of your business finances is crucial to your success. Introducing the new HSBC HK Business Express mobile app, another magnificent tool co-created by HSBC and our customers. Now, you can gain better control of your cash flow and receive financial insights tailored to your business needs anytime, anywhere.

Features and benefits
•	Secured and easy access: Mobile Security Key or biometric logon through fingerprints or facial recognition
•	Simpler and faster payment: You can now make local and international payments on the go, and make it even easier by using Mobile Security Key instead of your physical Security Device. If your payee is in Hong Kong, you can make payments using their mobile number, email address, FPS ID or by scanning a QR code. Once completed, you can tap to save or share a copy of the payment confirmation
•	Pay bills: Settle various types of bills including public utilities, government organisations and insurance companies
•	Smarter FX solutions: Tailored FX insights and instant quotes for multiple currencies
•	User-friendly navigation: View all your accounts on one single page
•	Effortless tracking: Check the real-time status of recent payments in details, end-to-end from HSBC to the beneficiary bank
•	Instant help: Message our customer service officers for any enquiry, including account-specific information. You can view the conversations at any time
•	If you are a user of Microsoft Dynamics 365 Business Central, you can now go to HSBC Smart Solution and use the app to make payments to vendors in your payment journals

Download HSBC HK Business Express now to stay on top of your business finances.

* Important Note:
This App is provided by The Hongkong and Shanghai Banking Corporation Limited (‘HSBC HK’) for the use of HSBC HK customers only. If you (or the entity you represent, as applicable) are not our HSBC HK customer, please leave this App. If you attempt or continue to access or use this App, you (or the entity you represent, as applicable) will be deemed to have confirmed you are our HSBC HK customer, agreed to our applicable terms and conditions and complied with the applicable laws and regulations of competent jurisdictions in connection with the use of this App.

apps.title: SimplyWise: Receipts, Expenses
apps.description:
All-in-one solution for effortless expense management, receipts scanning, tax refund optimization.

Simplify your financial life with the most accurate receipt scanner, one-tap filing & expense categorization, smart reminders for tax deductions, instant expense reports, and more. 

AI-DRIVEN RECEIPT SCANNER 
• Scan and store receipts, bills, invoices, and important paperwork effortlessly with our AI-driven receipt scanner.
• Capture key information, including store name, date, tip, sales tax, and total with our AI-driven receipt scanner.
• Get notified of upcoming return deadlines based on store policies with smart reminders. 

YOUR DIGITAL EXPENSE MANAGER
• Search and find what you need instantly, whether by expense category, store, or custom note.
• Track spending with monthly and yearly expense reports by category.
• Send PDFs, JPEGs, or Excel spreadsheets with ease via text or email. 

IMPORT RECEIPTS AUTOMATICALLY
• Automatically import business receipts from your email and online accounts (Gmail, Outlook, Amazon, Walmart, PayPal) by connecting them to SimplyWise.

MAXIMIZE TAX REFUND
• Turn your receipts into PDFs and organized spreadsheets categorized by expenses with just one tap. 
• Easily identify potential tax write-offs, so you make the most of every tax deduction.

SEAMLESS INTEGRATION
• Connect with bank or credit card accounts to match receipts with transactions, and automatically flag discrepancies.

UNLIMITED STORAGE & BANK-LEVEL SECURITY
• All documents are stored in a secure and unlimited cloud with 256-bit encryption.

◆ Loved by professionals, best phone call app, no annoying ads, complete privacy.
◆ HIPAA compliance secure texting with Business Associate Agreement - BAA.
◆ Financial compliance with call recording and text archiving capabilities.
◆ Local USA, Canada or 1800 Toll-free phone number with calling & secure texting.
◆ Phone tree, Auto-Attendant with virtual receptionist and forwarding extensions. 
◆ Cheap with low cost international calls to over 200 countries.
◆ Global call forwarding to multiple phone numbers.
◆ International roaming.
◆ Displays the caller id phone number .
◆ Personalized free voicemail. 
◆ Great carrier grade reliable voice quality.
◆ Low cost voip domestic and international calling and texting.
◆ Send pictures, audio and video.
◆ Works with Wi-fi or 3G/4G/LTE worldwide.
◆ Port or transfer your existing number to iPlum. 
◆ Pay As You Go or Unlimited plans. 
◆ Available in 22 global languages on iPhone & iPads.
◆ Built and supported in California, USA. 

iPlum brings powerful communication features right to your smartphone.

iPlum keeps your privacy by separating your business and personal communications. iPlum is a free app to download without any annoying ads.  Your data is secure.

Developed in California, trusted by businesses worldwide and featured in Entrepreneur Magazine.
                                                  ________________________________________

iPlum is the most affordable way for individuals and small businesses to add a dedicated business line to their smartphones. 


What can iPlum do for you and your business?
●	Flexibility: Take your business communication wherever you are and stay productive while on the go. If you’re a professional, small business owner or business traveler, wherever you’re at you’ll be able to stay connected, in contact and productive by ensuring access to your important business calls, texts, and voicemails.
●	Privacy: Keep your personal and business life separate with a dedicated business line on your smartphone.
●	HIPAA Compliance: Enable secure texting between doctor and patient with privacy and peace of mind.
●	Domestic or International: You can be a user living in U.S.A , Canada or International country.  Anyone can have iPlum and get the dedicated second phone number on their mobile.
●	Save money: All the features of a traditional business phone system like Phone tree, Auto-Attendant with virtual receptionist and forwarding extensions for low cost. No roaming charges or long term contracts. iPlum offers a pay as you go system with local and international calls or text.


iPlum is:
●	Easy to use: Get up and running in a few minutes without any new hardware to configure or purchase.
●	Reliable: The app is engineered to adapt to available data rates and latency of a broad range of Wi-Fi or cellular data channels.
●	Affordable: Unlimited US/Canada toll-free calling. Pay as you go and purchase additional credits as needed.


Subscriptions
For your convenience, the monthly subscriptions will be charged to your iTunes account and renews automatically 24 hours before the end of the current period at the same costs unless auto-renew is turned off by you in your iTunes account.

Privacy policy & Terms of Use:  https://iplum.com/privacy/

About iPlum
iPlum is a mobile technology company based in California USA. Dedicated to building great products, iPlum is finding innovative ways to simplify business communication for its customers. 

Contact Us
We are happy to hear your feedback and help you solve any iPlum issues. Just email us at help@iplum.com, and we'll respond to you promptly.

●	Save money: All the features of a traditional business phone system like Phone tree, Auto-Attendant with virtual receptionist and forwarding extensions for low cost. No roaming charges or long term contracts. iPlum offers a pay as you go system with local and international calls or text.


iPlum is:
●	Easy to use: Get up and running in a few minutes without any new hardware to configure or purchase.
●	Reliable: The app is engineered to adapt to available data rates and latency of a broad range of Wi-Fi or cellular data channels.
●	Affordable: Unlimited US/Canada toll-free calling. Pay as you go and purchase additional credits as needed.


Subscriptions
For your convenience, the monthly subscriptions will be charged to your iTunes account and renews automatically 24 hours before the end of the current period at the same costs unless auto-renew is turned off by you in your iTunes account.

iPlum is a mobile technology company based in California USA. Dedicated to building great products, iPlum is finding innovative ways to simplify business communication for its customers.

apps.title: GoCanvas - Business Forms
apps.description:
Easily digitize your workflows with a simple, user-friendly form builder. Streamline processes and enhance efficiency with digital forms. 

The most common forms users digitize:
- Inspections
- Invoices
- Quality Control
- Work Orders
- Scheduling & Dispatch
- Safety

Easy to build. Simple to use.

You have access to over 30,000 pre-built forms. Using the intuitive drag-and-drop technology, you can easily customize these templates to meet your specific requirements. The flexibility puts the power in your hands, giving you full control over your workflows.

Customers love us for:

- Scheduling & Dispatch
- Image & Video Capture
- Project Management
- Multi-person workflows
- Auto-fill & Calculations
- Offline Access
- GPS Tracking
- Barcode Scanning
- If/Then Logic

Terms of Service:
https://www.gocanvas.com/about-us/gocanvas-terms-of-service

Privacy Policy:
https://www.gocanvas.com/about-us/gocanvas-privacy-policy

Who We Are

GoCanvas®, part of the Nemetschek Group, is committed to transforming how businesses connect their office and field workers. Our user-friendly platforms aim to simplify inspections, digitize traditional paper-based processes, improve safety, and ensure maximum compliance with industry standards.

GoCanvas mobile and cloud solutions are designed to streamline data collection from the field to the office, taking care of administrative tasks so our customers can focus on what matters most — ensuring the safety of their teams, maintaining the integrity of their equipment, and operating more efficiently.

Since 2008, GoCanvas has been driven by a commitment to excellence and continuous innovation. Based in Reston, Virginia, and operating three distinct platforms—GoCanvas, Device Magic, and SiteDocs — we are trusted by thousands of companies to optimize their operations and deliver fast, high-quality results.
